title: Pennsylvania Department of Health, Drug Alcohol Treatment Facilities, Pennsylvania, 2007
name: Pennsylvania Department of Health, Drug Alcohol Treatment Facilities, Pennsylvania, 2007
description:
Abstract:

PA Drug and Alcohol Treatment Centers from the PA Dept of Health's quality assurance database.  Current as of 10/25/2007.

Purpose:

This layer was developed for use in emergency situations and for the general public.

Supplemental_Information:

The drug and alcohol treatment center addresses were geocoded.  Geocoding of addresses creates points of estimated locations.  These locations were not verified.  The user should assume that there is some spatial error.
